# Agent Bridge

This project uses a git-native handoff protocol. Follow it on every session.

## Session start

Read before any work:

1. `.agent/HANDOFF.md`
2. `.agent/state.json`

## Session end

Before finishing, update:

1. `.agent/state.json` — stage status, actor, timestamp, artifacts
2. `.agent/HANDOFF.md` — sections: Current stage, Done, Next step, Do not touch
3. Commit `.agent/` (message: `agent: handoff <stage>`)

Full protocol: `AGENTS.md`
